41:21.263 --> 41:33.416
and how that made him happy to know that the people that he gave that knowledge to could go out with that and be able to restore those old buildings and go back to their natural behavior.

41:33.436 --> 41:38.401
Did you get a set of those 12 volumes that they presented, the FBI did?

41:38.562 --> 41:41.204
The 12 volumes, I guess they itemized.

41:41.385 --> 41:47.271
There were 12 volumes that they presented in the court yesterday or the day before.

41:47.825 --> 41:55.172
It was a 12-volume catalog, essentially, a computerized catalog of the books that they removed from a tumble... No, I would like to get a set of those.

41:55.232 --> 41:55.813
Well, I would, too.

41:55.893 --> 41:56.073
I should.

41:56.093 --> 41:59.656
I was wondering, I mean, yeah, that's the catalog of your... Yeah, I should.

42:00.117 --> 42:00.978
Well, wouldn't you think so?

42:00.998 --> 42:02.419
I mean, I'm desperate to get a set of them.

