double check it and see that's in July but there there's some people. I would just say that there's a possibility it would be good if you checked it again, something like that. Well they haven't given me any additional updated stuff to check. How many of these instances of things like this did you see? Oh I'd have to look at the book in case there were multiple copies but four or five instances of that a major rarity is going to the wrong institution

44:12.882 --> 44:14.504
You can't think of any other roughhands.

44:14.524 --> 44:16.647
Well, I can, but I'll maybe.

44:17.608 --> 44:18.309
Come on, come on for me.

44:18.369 --> 44:19.271
No, I'll wait.

44:20.172 --> 44:22.335
I need some bargaining chips, you know.

